ting the feasibility of requiring annotations on only a few\nimages in a new domain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 26 Nov 2022 18:41:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2023 03:08:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-21"}
